{"tid":644353,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"假設全世界好似香港咁逼","createTime":"2018-04-27T07:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T18:31:06.000Z","uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db5d79ad158ce2afc834b7e03b673bd7ce17a83c","tid":644353,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"假設全世界好似香港咁逼<br />\n世界人口約10000億人<br />\n（世界面積1.5億平方公里，香港人口密度每平方公里6700人）<br />\n<br />\n假設全世界好似港島咁逼<br />\n世界人口約2.2萬億人<br />\n（港島人口密度每平方公里15000人）<br />\n<br />\n假設全世界好似九龍咁逼<br />\n世界人口約6.6萬億人<br />\n（港島人口密度每平方公里45000人）<br />\n<br />\n假設全世界好似天水圍咁逼<br />\n世界人口約10萬億人<br />\n（港島人口密度每平方公里70000人）<br />\n<br />\n結論，香港真係好撚逼。"},{"pid":"4252b84ce2fa9f74e4931ea8b091f7160304b57c","tid":644353,"uid":58140,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6c39363d5e7311c045f716f8c28dca1f736440","tid":644353,"uid":150716,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4252b84ce2fa9f74e4931ea8b091f7160304b57c","tid":644353,"uid":58140,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"樓主想拎香港好逼黎打個飛機姐 我估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ea1bb59bf2da9488975fc736e39f1b8174d97b","tid":644353,"uid":112416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:22:26.000Z","msg":"咁如果全世界好似地鐵車箱咁迫呢?"},{"pid":"05586a6c3a3d7df067253ff3384804cc695945ea","tid":644353,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:13:09.000Z","msg":"心中香港理想人口<br />\n<br />\n如果<br />\n港島區人口密度10000人<br />\n九龍半島15000人<br />\n荃灣、葵青、將軍澳各10萬人<br />\n大嶼山20萬人<br />\n新界（除大嶼山、荃灣、葵青、將軍澳）1000人<br />\n<br />\nThen<br />\n港島 80 萬人<br />\n九龍 75 萬人<br />\n新界 80 萬人<br />\n荃灣、葵青、將軍澳 30 萬人<br />\n大嶼山 20萬人<br />\n<br />\nTotal 285萬人"},{"pid":"0b17db30d5335b1c59b4f587ddc937ea7f7f49be","tid":644353,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e6c39363d5e7311c045f716f8c28dca1f736440","tid":644353,"uid":150716,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4252b84ce2fa9f74e4931ea8b091f7160304b57c","tid":644353,"uid":58140,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"樓主想拎香港好逼黎打個飛機姐 我估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"想叫政府，不要再鼓勵生育，同埋唔 好收咁多新移民。<br />\n<br />\n唔好現在咁快就學新加坡/當年曾陰權咁，鼓勵生育。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲、加拿大、新西蘭、蒙古就要鼓勵生育。<br />\n<br />\n最好笑係新加坡，日本，香港，台灣，明明係逼到九彩的國家，政府竟然走去叫人生多些。"},{"pid":"414c498e175e16a4099e0a8d72ad54dbef761e44","tid":644353,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T11:37:54.000Z","msg":"香港需要滅霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53b602e7782fa709ef3ca899ec965db80853d3c","tid":644353,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b17db30d5335b1c59b4f587ddc937ea7f7f49be","tid":644353,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e6c39363d5e7311c045f716f8c28dca1f736440","tid":644353,"uid":150716,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4252b84ce2fa9f74e4931ea8b091f7160304b57c","tid":644353,"uid":58140,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"樓主想拎香港好逼黎打個飛機姐 我估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"想叫政府，不要再鼓勵生育，同埋唔 好收咁多新移民。<br />\n<br />\n唔好現在咁快就學新加坡/當年曾陰權咁，鼓勵生育。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲、加拿大、新西蘭、蒙古就要鼓勵生育。<br />\n<br />\n最好笑係新加坡，日本，香港，台